On Day 4 of my project, I created a 3D donut and a cup using Blender. I started by making the basic donut shape by using torus tool option and
then adjusted it to look more natural and smooth.
After that, I added the icing on top and shaped it to look like it is slightly dripping, which made the donut look more realistic and 
using cylinder shape I made a cup and then I added colors and materials to give the donut and cup a real look. 
I also worked on lighting and camera angles to get a good final render. 
This project helped me understand the basics of modeling, texturing, and rendering in Blender.

I have experienced a lot in this project this project is a work of patience and focus . It's great to see the work of yours into moving object.
